24:26.553 --> 24:39.873
made a famous book called The Library of Mirio Biblon who made the summary of a hundred or more books.

24:41.215 --> 24:52.712
Many of these books are lost and so they remain only in the summary and made by this patriarch who also has transcribed some

24:53.317 --> 24:54.358
part of these books.

24:54.458 --> 25:04.130
And so many, many books remain in these, in this compilation of thoughts.

25:04.531 --> 25:08.916
And there are, what else, many, many other things of this quality.

25:09.156 --> 25:17.907
